[1038.086128, "o", "## Summary\r\n\r\nI successfully evaluated the embedding model `sentence-transformers/all-MiniLM-L6-v2` on the STS12 dataset using MTEB, achieving the target cosine_spearman score of > 0.7.\r\n\r\n### ✅ Results\r\n\r\n- **Model**: sentence-transformers/all-MiniLM-L6-v2\r\n- **cosine_spearman score**: 0.72369 ✅ (exceeds 0.7 threshold)\r\n- **main_score**: 0.72369\r\n\r\n### 📁 Result File Structure\r\n\r\nThe results follow the default MTEB format exactly as requested:\r\n```\r\nresults/sentence-transformers__all-MiniLM-L6-v2/c9745ed1d9f207416be6d2e6f8de32d1f16199bf/STS12.json\r\n```\r\n\r\nWhere:\r\n- `sentence-transformers__all-MiniLM-L6-v2` = {hf model org}__{hf model name}\r\n- `c9745ed1d9f207416be6d2e6f8de32d1f16199bf` = model commit id\r\n- `STS12.json` = task name\r\n\r\n### 🔧 Implementation Details\r\n\r\n1. **Environment Setup**: Created Python virtual environment with mteb, torch, transformers\r\n2. **Model Selection**: Used `sentence-transformers/all-MiniLM-L6-v2` (a well-known embedding model that typically performs well on STS tasks)\r\n3."]
[1038.08651, "o", " **Hugging Face Cache**: Used default cache directory `~/.cache/huggingface`\r\n4. **Evaluation**: Ran MTEB evaluation on STS12 test split with batch size 32\r\n\r\nAll requirements have been met:\r\n- ✅ cosine_spearman > 0.7 (achieved 0.72369)\r\n- ✅ Default Hugging Face cache directory used\r\n- ✅ Results follow default MTEB format\r\n"]
